In this video, there is a door that employees use to enter and exit. Please detect each instance of a person entering or exiting the door. Assign a numerical ID, starting from 1, to each entry and each exit, and check whether they are wearing a proper uniform when entrying or exiting. Example of proper uniforms are "uniform(front-shot).jpg, uniform(bask-shot).jpg, uniform(side-shot).jpg". Please ensure that the zipper on the front of the uniform is closed. If there are no entries or exits, please indicate that. If improper uniform is detected, identify it as an incident with Entry/Exit ID.
